sections.title: Biz Events Lab: Get the buy and sell biz events
Biz Events Lab: Summarize Trading Volume by Account and Type

input.value:
fetch bizevents
| filter event.type=="com.easytrade.buy-assets" or event.type=="com.easytrade.sell-assets"
| summarize sumTradingVolume=sum(amount), by:{accountId, event.type}
| sort sumTradingVolume desc

grail.canonicalQuery:
fetch bizevents
| filter event.type == "com.easytrade.buy-assets" OR event.type == "com.easytrade.sell-assets"
| summarize by:{accountId, event.type}, sum(amount), alias:sumTradingVolume
| sort sumTradingVolume, direction:"descending"
grail.query:
fetch bizevents
| filter event.type=="com.easytrade.buy-assets" or event.type=="com.easytrade.sell-assets"
| summarize sumTradingVolume=sum(amount), by:{accountId, event.type}
| sort sumTradingVolume desc

input.value:
fetch bizevents
| filter event.type=="com.easytrade.buy-assets" or event.type=="com.easytrade.sell-assets"
| summarize sumTradingVolume=sum(amount), by:{accountId, event.type}
| sort sumTradingVolume desc

grail.canonicalQuery:
fetch bizevents
| filter event.type == "com.easytrade.sell-assets" OR event.type == "com.easytrade.buy-assets"
| parse event.type, "'com.easytrade.' ALPHA:tradeType"
| summarize by:{bin(timestamp, 15m)}, {{countIf(tradeType == "buy"), alias:buy}, {countIf(tradeType == "sell"), alias:sell}}
